Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Đứng dậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bái tiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cung chúc.
